![Dartboard Logo](http://dartboardanalytics.com/img/logo-dark.png)
## Welcome to Dartboard.
Dartboard is a business intelligence and analytics service to help early and growth stage businesses make sense of volumes of historical and disparate data.

### What's this?
This is a placeholder site, meant to list code repos we've open-sourced. We'll add those repos very soon!

### Contact
If you've got questions, please reach out to us at tech@dartboardanalytics.com.
